{
  "stem": "232.4",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were going-- we were in the train and, at this moment, when I was in the train, I realized I was no more child.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It-- it became to me like you take away a-- a curtain, that this is the real thing, that, here, something is going to happen.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were in the train.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We came after eight days.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We arrived in Birkenau.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Of course, we didn't know at this time it was Birkenau.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We arrived.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They opened the-- the doors from the train.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I saw a round gate and a platform with-- it looks to me like monkeys, a lot of the inmates, with striped pajamas and the Germans with the-- with their black boots and pens.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[SPEAKING GERMAN] And right away, they separated women from men and-- and-- and pushed in a corner.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And here were all the men standing, and SS men with a whip, with a horse whip, came and touched, touched men on the-- on the shoulder.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And, immediately, there was a inmate, pulled him away to another corner.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So he went about 12 times, 12 people were pulled out from this transport, 12 men.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was standing the last one.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My dad, when he jumped, he left the coat, the long coat on with a shawl over my face.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the SS men asked me what is this.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Is this a girl or a boy?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I says, [SPEAKING GERMAN], means I am a man, not a female.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So he touched with a whip and put me-- and I was the-- 13.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And father of my friend Rudy Goldman, 14 people were chosen in one corner.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the rest were pushed together with the-- right away with the men and women, put out-- put back on trucks, and taken away.",
      "word_count": 24
    }
  ],
